  {
    index: 1,
    name: "Realm Code",
    description: "Startup advisory",
    quote: "We have been working with Ključna Reč Digital for the past year and have seen a significant increase in social media engagement of our clients. Their team is professional and truly cares about our success."
  },
  {
    index: 2,
    name: "nuvo",
    description: "B2B SaaS",
    quote: "Milica’s technical videos on LinkedIn were a game changer for our niche audience, driving engagement and boosting visibility. She knows how to simplify complex ideas into clear, impactful content. Highly recommend her expertise!"
  },
  {
    index: 3,
    name: "Tamara",
    description: "Jungle Pet",
    quote: "Milica je jako kreativna i pristupačna osoba. Sama je osmislila scenario, dovela psa glumca, snimila video, i pomogla nam da se izdvojimo od konkurencije u kraju. Zahvaljujući njoj, naš pet shop je postao mnogo prepoznatljiviji. Preporučujemo je svakom ko želi kvalitetan sadržaj!"
  },
  {
