    description: "E-commerce Manager at 123 Shop",
    quote: "Their social media marketing strategies helped us build a strong community around our brand. Engagement rates soared, and so did our sales."
  },
  {
    index: 5,
    name: "Johanna Jana",
    description: "Digital Strategist at Tech Innovators",
    quote: "The analytics and tracking implemented by Ključna Reč Digital provided invaluable insights. We now make data-informed decisions that drive real results."
